---
description: Enforce Next.js App Router best practices and performance
globs: ["app/**/*", "components/**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

## NEXT.JS RULES

- Use App Router correctly
- Default to Server Components
- Use "use client" only when necessary

## PERFORMANCE

- Optimize images with next/image
- Use dynamic imports when needed
- Keep bundle size small

## SEO

- Use metadata properly
- Use semantic HTML

## STRUCTURE

- app/ for routes
- components/ for reusable UI
- Keep logic separated from UI

## STATIC EXPORT

- Ensure compatibility with static export
- Avoid server-only features
